<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>救生艇新闻：博客——保护人类</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 05 Mar 2026 01:07:41 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>在玻璃上进行激光写入，实现密集、快速、高效的档案数据存储</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/laser-writing-in-glass-for-dense-fast-and-efficient-archival-data-storage</link><description>基于飞秒激光玻璃直写的光学档案存储技术解决了档案存储的实际需求。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/laser-writing-in-glass-for-dense-fast-and-efficient-archival-data-storage.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Mar 2026 01:07:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/laser-writing-in-glass-for-dense-fast-and-efficient-archival-data-storage</guid></item><item><title>生物分子凝聚体的动态和异质组成及其功能相关性</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/the-dynamic-and-heterogeneous-composition-of-biomolecular-condensates-and-its-functional-relevance</link><description>生物分子凝聚物是控制各种生物过程的非膜封装隔室。最近的研究表明，凝结物会随着时间的推移而对刺激做出反应。本综述讨论了核和细胞质凝聚物的异质性和组成变化、它们的调节以及这些变化如何影响细胞生化反应。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/the-dynamic-and-heterogeneous-composition-of-biomolecular-condensates-and-its-functional-relevance.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Mar 2026 00:52:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/the-dynamic-and-heterogeneous-composition-of-biomolecular-condensates-and-its-functional-relevance</guid></item><item><title>推动溜冰场可持续发展的内幕</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/inside-the-push-to-make-ice-rinks-sustainable</link><description>多伦多城市大学的可持续材料化学家 Stefania Impellizzeri 正在尝试通过微调水化学和溜冰场相关材料来使溜冰场更加高效和可持续。&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/inside-the-push-to-make-ice-rinks-sustainable.webp" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Mar 2026 00:37:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/inside-the-push-to-make-ice-rinks-sustainable</guid></item><item><title>前沿：饮食限制 (DR)</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/frontiers-dietary-restriction-dr</link><description>定义为减少热量摄入或选择性限制特定营养素而不造成营养不良，是已知可延长物种寿命和健康寿命的最强有力的干预措施之一。从酵母到哺乳动物的研究表明，DR 会引发保守的遗传、转录和表观遗传程序，从而促进细胞维持和抗应激能力。在分子水平上，DR 涉及进化上保守的营养感应途径，包括胰岛素/IGF-1 信号传导 (IIS)、雷帕霉素的机制靶点 (mTOR)、AMP 激活蛋白激酶 (AMPK) 和 NAD&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/frontiers.webp" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Mar 2026 00:22:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/frontiers-dietary-restriction-dr</guid></item><item><title>SNAP25经历相分离以促进突触小泡融合机器的组装</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/snap25-undergoes-phase-separation-to-facilitate-the-assembly-of-the-synaptic-vesicle-fusion-machinery</link><description>朱等人。发现 SNAP25（参与突触小泡融合的关键 SNARE 蛋白）发生相分离，这是通过棕榈酰化修饰和与 Syntaxin-1 相互作用来调节的。 SNAP25 凝聚体招募 Syntaxin-1 和 VAMP2 形成凝聚层，促进囊泡对接和 SNARE 复合物的组装。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/snap25-undergoes-phase-separation-to-facilitate-the-assembly-of-the-synaptic-vesicle-fusion-machinery2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Mar 2026 00:07:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/snap25-undergoes-phase-separation-to-facilitate-the-assembly-of-the-synaptic-vesicle-fusion-machinery</guid></item><item><title>人工智能有可能吞噬商业软件——它可能会改变我们的工作方式</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/ai-threatens-to-eat-business-software-and-it-could-change-the-way-we-work</link><description>最近几周，包括 Salesforce、ServiceNow 和 Oracle 在内的一系列大型“软件即服务”公司的股价暴跌。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/ai-threatens-to-eat-business-software-and-it-could-change-the-way-we-work.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Mar 2026 23:52:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/ai-threatens-to-eat-business-software-and-it-could-change-the-way-we-work</guid></item><item><title>研究概述了 JWST 和 Ariel 如何在系外行星大气层上进行合作</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/study-outlines-how-jwst-and-ariel-could-team-up-on-exoplanet-atmospheres</link><description>天文学家希望使用尽可能多的系统收集尽可能多的数据。有时这需要仪器之间的协调。一旦詹姆斯·韦伯太空望远镜 (JWST) 和即将到来的大气遥感红外系外行星大型勘测 (Ariel) 任务的团队在 2030 年代初期投入运行，他们将有很多机会实现这一目标。 Ariel-JWST 协同工作组在 arXiv 上预印了一篇新论文，详细介绍了这两个系统如何协同工作以更好地分析系外行星。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/study-outlines-how-jwst-and-ariel-could-team-up-on-exoplanet-atmospheres.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Mar 2026 23:37:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/study-outlines-how-jwst-and-ariel-could-team-up-on-exoplanet-atmospheres</guid></item><item><title>加密：数字未来的关键守护者</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/encryption-a-key-guardian-of-our-digital-future</link><description>作者：查克·布鲁克斯和比尔·鲍尔斯。&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/encryption-a-key-guardian-of-our-digital-future.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Mar 2026 23:22:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/encryption-a-key-guardian-of-our-digital-future</guid></item><item><title>使用礼宾护理模式通过 Lifespan.MD 增强长寿医学</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/using-concierge-care-models-to-enhance-longevity-medicine-with-lifespan-md</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Mar 2026 23:07:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/using-concierge-care-models-to-enhance-longevity-medicine-with-lifespan-md</guid></item><item><title>这个人想要参观黑洞。他以 1/3 光速达到目标的激进计划</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/this-man-wants-to-visit-a-black-hole-inside-his-radical-plan-to-reach-it-at-1-3-the-speed-of-light</link><description>它是如此狂野，以至于它可能会起作用。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/this-man-wants-to-visit-a-black-hole-inside-his-radical-plan-to-reach-it-at-1-3-the-speed-of-light2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Mar 2026 22:52:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isP